# 🔧 ISTP – The Fixer Agent: Full Marketing Playbook

---

## 🧠 1️⃣ Psychological Summary

The **ISTP Realtor Archetype: The Fixer Agent** is the rugged, no-nonsense pro who gets their hands dirty. You’re tactical, practical, and thrive on solving tough problems — from walking distressed properties to negotiating repairs that turn a profit.

**Psychological Edge:**  
- *Hands-On Tactician:* You’re not afraid of roll-up-your-sleeves challenges — your buyers love that you see opportunities where others see headaches.
- *Analytical Repair Pro:* You break down a property like a mechanic diagnoses an engine — your clients trust you for honest, practical advice.
- *DIY Credibility:* Contractors, DIY flippers, and budget-minded investors love you because you think like them.

**Market Fit:**  
- Fixer-uppers, distressed properties, contractor deals.
- Older homes, transitional neighborhoods, rural flips.

---

## ✨ 2️⃣ Personal Brand & Social Persona

**Brand Vibe:**  
- Rugged, industrial, down-to-earth. Neutral grays, dark denim blues, steel accents.
- Real photos — no fluff: tool belt shots, before-and-after reno pics, walkthrough videos.
- Fonts: bold, industrial sans-serif, punchy text overlays.

**Core Channels & Plays:**  
- **Instagram & TikTok:** Quick DIY reno tips, tool reviews, “How I Saved $20K On This Flip.”
- **YouTube:** “Fixer Breakdown” series — deep dives into inspection finds, repair strategies.
- **Facebook Groups:** Local investor and DIY home improvement forums.

**Content Rhythm:**  
- Weekly project updates — your community wants to see progress.
- Reels: “What To Watch For When Buying A Fixer.”
- Q&A Lives: “Ask Me Anything About Flips & Repairs.”

---

## 🔑 3️⃣ Go-To-Market Strategy & Partnerships

**📣 Campaigns:**  
- Google Ads: “Looking For A Fixer-Upper? Work With The Hands-On Pro.”
- Local SEO: “Best Agent For Contractors & DIY Investors.”

**🤝 Partnerships:**  
- Align with local tradespeople — plumbers, roofers, electricians — create a trusted vendor list.
- Host investor meetups at renovation sites — show the work in progress.
- Build a “Fixer Squad” with contractors to bundle deals for buyers.

**📩 Client Loyalty & Nurture:**  
- Monthly “Reno Report” newsletter — highlight deals, pitfalls, ROI examples.
- Exclusive early-bird walk-throughs on new fixer listings.
- Client spotlights: before-and-after pics with cost breakdowns.

---

## 🔧 What Sets the Fixer Agent Apart

✅ You walk the talk — you know what it really takes to fix and flip.  
✅ Buyers & investors see you as a trusted boots-on-the-ground advisor.  
✅ You simplify complicated projects with practical, realistic strategies.

